snippet.title: PokeMMO Brings out the Best in Pokémon
snippet.description:
Is PokeMMO is the best Pokemon game ever made? What can Gamefreak can learn from their past?

0:00 - Intro
1:24 - Introducing PokeMMO
2:30 - Hardware Needed
2:46 - PokeMMO
4:38 - How to download PokeMMO
5:49- How to improve newer Pokemon games
8:12 - Outro

Discord: https://discord.gg/UZckNZ67Jt
Twitter: https://twitter.com/owlbit8
PokeMMO Website: https://pokemmo.eu/

Software Used:

Editing: Kinemaster
Script: Google Docs
Audio: Audacity

#PokemonMMO
#Pokemon

(Music Used, in order of appearance) 

Welcome Theme - Pokemon Let’s go Pikachu/Eevee

Mt. Coronet (Remastered) - Zame 

Pokemon: Kazoo Edition - Mr. TopHatter

Wild Area (Version 2) - Pokemon Sword and Shield

Pokemon Theme EPIC VERSION - L'Orchestra Cinématique

S.S ANNE (Remastered) - Zame

Pasio Mountains - Pokemon Masters

Rival Encounter - Pokemon Fire Red/Leaf Green

Sootopolis City (RSE) - Qumu

Pallet Town (Remastered) - Zame

Pokemon DP Lake Theme - GlitchxCity

Battle! Champion Rival Music - Pokemon Fire Red/Leaf Green

Humilau City Gym (Remastered) Pokemon Black and White - Zame

Poke & Chill: Hau’oli City - Mikel

National Park Remastered - Zame

Pokemon Battle Tower Theme - Pokemon Sword and Shield

Pokemon Sun and Moon - Hau’oli City (Night) - Pokemon Sun and Moon

Sinnoh Route 201 (Remastered) Pokemon Diamond and Pearl - Zame

Coconut Mall - Mario Kart Wii

Relic Song (Remastered) Pokemon Black and White - Zame

Pokemon Route 216 Arrangement - Lazy Totodile
